title: The Fresh Out In Columbus Comedy Special w/ Dcyoungfly, KarlousMiller & ChicoBean | Ep. 201
itunes:title: The Fresh Out In Columbus Comedy Special w/ Dcyoungfly, KarlousMiller & ChicoBean | Ep. 201
description:
FOLLOW THE CREW On this special episode comedians DC Young Fly, Karlous Miller and Chico Bean show love in Columbus, Ohio but first they gotta deal with the fan who just got out of prison! You already know the crew can handle any situation with poise and jokes! Plus the whole audience got roasted!!! be sure to get your tickets for the 85 South Show at The Apollo! https://www1.ticketmaster.com/85-sout...
